d":"0120e742456cfa1db14fa033ac09e95fafeb476c","tid":1506790,"uid":181502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:25:25.000Z","msg":"邊個再捉鬼，我就成team人屌柒佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:26:55.000Z","msg":"再比人捉鬼<br />\n真係會被team kill"},{"pid":"460b11114d4b61feb4d5d3a721dea687cf967edc","tid":1506790,"uid":7270,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:27:11.000Z","msg":"琴晚見到咩頭盔痴膠紙就係鬼，但明明係最做得嘢班手足打緊狗，真係激撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a1f440e017fed0c1323d7422a4b67ba6bd9da32","tid":1506790,"uid":50904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:28:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>[濕L晒，你要驚]防毒濾棉濕哂水會打柴，請立即更換</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1506772\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1506772</a><br />\n整合左啲濕水對濾棉影響嘅資料，大家幫手入去推比更多手足睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">利申:唔係呢方面專家，只係問人+整合資料，需要人實測</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n琴日落左成日大雨，好多裝修師傅都被迫做左海底奇兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然濾棉有一定「抗水」能力去過濾有毒蒸汽，但係「唉屌濕撚晒」之下都會打柴<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">為防TL;DR 先寫結論:<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n1. 外露濾棉如 2297/2097 + 單罐豬嘴3311K 等，如濕哂請即更換<br />\n2. 如501蓋 + 5N11 有外殼包下嘅，請打開檢查有無全濕<br />\n3. 內置濾棉嘅綜合濾罐 如60926/3系列，正路入水位唔多，但好睇實際有幾濕<br />\n4. 單純濾罐部份 如6006/3 系列，活性碳唔吸水，乾返應該唔大影響，有待實測<br />\n5. 雨天環境，重課可考慮502蓋 + 3M 7093 有殼防水式P100濾棉"},{"pid":"e02cb6aa616f429ef829bc626d472ca8c8449229","tid":1506790,"uid":159448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:31:03.000Z","msg":"點解會捉鬼 係因為由頭到尾都無認同前線做既野 不割蓆只係口號"},{"pid":"01a2eaaf0ff9719b7580a7c17b1b7fe999b6513f","tid":1506790,"uid":293355,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:31:18.000Z","msg":"幫推，見到d人話咩粉紅就係鬼，白痴<br />\n最前線既朋友都有組隊，label可能只係辦認自己既隊員<br />\n話人係鬼既十成自己無做過前線。"},{"pid":"dd90fe7a1a13691c962c1a4f70d0c034557b138a","tid":1506790,"uid":145496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:34:10.000Z","msg":"無錯，果班打狗咁大力，邊會係鬼"},{"pid":"4aede0eefc360e6ea987a746d04091e5178a911d","tid":1506790,"uid":107596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:36:42.000Z","msg":"影還影 唔好影到大頭就得"},{"pid":"80f8510b6a32d9a81e13e245c1f5af2f0d8a5afe","tid":1506790,"uid":138282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:45:00.000Z","msg":"其實不割蓆唔係得個講字<br />\n係要做咖各位"},{"pid":"c10cf446b2598b4b86203f6478a59fd8da654354","tid":1506790,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:52:59.000Z","msg":"P<br />\n<br />\nI<br />\n<br />\nS<br />\n<br />\nH<br />\n<br />\n！"},{"pid":"bdb7f3e7de711a84075308d7532420c00a1b8ab4","tid":1506790,"uid":131282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:54:00.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"d287ee872f15de3fbc8addd6b841cdcf8c421aba","tid":1506790,"uid":235655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:54:02.000Z","msg":"有實質證據就話姐<br />\n成班冷氣軍師 坐係屋企睇片當實地調查<br />\n冇證冇據屌你班柒頭係到擾亂軍心"},{"pid":"b96419f45108a4ee6fda9f3a77cff49dd95d91ea","tid":1506790,"uid":304321,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:57:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60becca0701b348734f60111565fd8b706eab3cd","tid":1506790,"uid":36158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:57:45.000Z","msg":"不要捉鬼"},{"pid":"06d51992d249dfdad2fafec3e419f7217d624759","tid":1506790,"uid":61712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:08:15.000Z","msg":"推啊 我屌你大J"},{"pid":"025cfa7f1e0471add84b0884c34f49e4855cb299","tid":1506790,"uid":61712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:08:36.000Z","msg":"推到上熱門 要澄清番班手足"},{"pid":"cd477b38fd28ac0737c56f337c7469f28ce308d1","tid":1506790,"uid":61712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:08:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c20e77743f659c00e751b219ee4a9f41ed7aa5f7","tid":1506790,"uid":61712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:09:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a7d382a3b2d1382c9018f364f436f12e9c8d16b","tid":1506790,"uid":61712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:09:25.000Z","msg":"不捉鬼 不分化"},{"pid":"8389e051d36044dfa68351f2e53260efed274f31","tid":1506790,"uid":282587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:13:15.000Z","msg":"一大堆未落過場連示威都未去過嘅智障只識系連登扮神探扮軍師，對連登呢個地方好失望。"},{"pid":"220b64672f7f40e6ba06ae2fe55ecc1ef9b79d1f","tid":1506790,"uid":61712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:15:53.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"3391c9900ea28defee25ef31e16c7f661935a8f4","tid":1506790,"uid":62025,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:18:02.000Z","msg":"from tg大消息group<br />\n<br />\n都係個句 捉鬼係毫無意義<br />\n只會破壞手足之間信任<br />\n要防鬼就自組一team人 互相照應 <br />\n確保走個陣唔好俾人㩒低就得<br />\n唔好再放心機係無謂野上面<br />\n<br />\n今日睇到個po真係好嬲<br />\n點解話極都唔醒😭😭<br />\n到依加都四圍forward緊"},{"pid":"819e2df091861760504adb6ea27931fde03f81a8","tid":1506790,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:19:13.000Z","msg":"捉鬼死全家"},{"pid":"e02762b4db378e0392559684b2f3849df461e979","tid":1506790,"uid":182802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:19:54.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n捉鬼等於推手足去死<br />\n唔好再捉"},{"pid":"e7eb65339a12fb5110c5b087c31a15859fc4c286","tid":1506790,"uid":281735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:22:07.000Z","msg":"除非攻擊自己人/平民，否則一律唔係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ebfa15e3cc9525be91c9c3b9108cdfa33922b40","tid":1506790,"uid":